Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT

Title: Authorizes a certain property operating as a private membership establishment to sell alcohol for on-premises consumption to members and their guests
Summary: Authorizes a certain property operating as a private membership establishment to sell alcohol for on-premises consumption to members and their guests; defines "private membership establishment".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to authorizing a certain property operating as a private membership establishment to sell alcohol for on-premises consumption to members and their guests
